VALUES ("Willy Wonka and the Chocolate Factory", "Charlie and 4 other children get the chance to tour Willy Wonka's mysterious chocolate factory", "assets/images/willyWonka/willyWonka.jpg", "The world is astounded when Willy Wonka, for years a recluse in his <<place>>, announces that 5 <<adjective>> children will be given a tour of the factory. ","The children will be shown all the secrets of his <<adjective>> <<noun>>, and one will win a lifetime supply of Wonka <<plural noun>>. ", "Nobody wants the prize more than young Charlie, but as his family is so <<adjective>> that buying even one <<noun>> is a treat, buying enough to find one of the five <<adjective>> tickets is unlikely in the extreme. ", "But in <<place>>, magic can happen. Charlie, along with four somewhat <<adjective>> other children, get the chance of a lifetime and a tour of the factory. ", "Along the way, mild disasters befall each of the <<adjective>> children. One child falls into a river made of <<plural noun>>. ", "Another turns into a <<adjective>> <<noun>> after chewing an experimental <<food>> containing a <<noun>>, despite Wonka's warnings. ", "Another falls down a garbage chute attempting to grab a <<adjective>> <<animal>> egg. ", "At the end of the tour, Charlie is the only child remaining. After a bit of <<verb ending in ing>>, Willy Wonka grants Charlie the ultimate gift, his <<noun>>. ", "", "", "/assets/images/willyWonka/segment1.jpg","/assets/images/willyWonka/segment2.jpg","/assets/images/willyWonka/segment3.jpg","/assets/images/willyWonka/segment4.jpg","/assets/images/willyWonka/segment5.jpg","/assets/images/willyWonka/segment6.jpg","/assets/images/willyWonka/segment7.jpg","/assets/images/willyWonka/segment8.jpeg",NULL,NULL, NOW(), NOW());